@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mrfrbq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.52 + v2 + 0.53)) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.09) * v0))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.56) - (tmp + 0.74 + v2 + 0.83)) + v2)
    v1 = 0.55
    v1 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.99 + tmp + 0.73)) - (v2 / v1))
    data[tid] = v0
